---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { projects } from '../data/portfolio';

const featured = projects.filter((p) => p.featured);
---

<PageLayout title="About" description="Platform Engineer — from sensor validation to Kubernetes clusters.">
  <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 tracking-wide uppercase mb-6">About</p>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">From silicon to K8s clusters.</h1>

  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none prose-slate prose-headings:font-semibold prose-headings:text-slate-900 prose-p:text-slate-600 prose-li:text-slate-600 prose-strong:text-slate-800">
    <p>
      My engineering journey started at the sensor level — validating image sensors, writing
      calibration routines in Matlab, and understanding how photons become pixels. From there I
      moved into middleware and backend systems, building data pipelines and APIs that connected
      hardware to business logic.
    </p>
    <p>
      Today I work as a Platform Engineer, designing and operating the infrastructure that
      development teams rely on. Kubernetes clusters, CI/CD pipelines, observability stacks,
      VPN meshes, and developer tooling — the invisible layer that makes shipping software
      possible.
    </p>

    <h2>How I work</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>No magic.</strong> If you can't explain it, you don't understand it.</li>
      <li><strong>Script everything.</strong> If you did it twice, automate it.</li>
      <li><strong>Write it down.</strong> Documentation is a feature, not a chore.</li>
      <li><strong>Own the metal.</strong> Understanding the hardware makes you a better cloud engineer.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Things I've built</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
    {featured.map((project) => (
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">{project.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">{project.description}</p>
        </div>
        {project.github && (
          <a
            href={project.github}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors whitespace-nowrap"
          >
            GitHub &rarr;
          </a>
        )}
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>

  <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-slate-100">
    <h2 class="text-sm text-slate-400 tracking-wide uppercase mb-4">Academic background</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
      My thesis work focused on image sensor characterization following the EMVA 1288 standard —
      measuring noise, linearity, and quantum efficiency at the pixel level. This experience with
      precision measurement and data analysis shaped how I approach infrastructure: measure first,
      optimize second.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
